    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required gradation level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved gradation 2 against a required gradation 3; this gap is accepted on the basis of corroborating analytical sensitivity analysis demonstrating that the single test configuration is representative of the governing load case. The overall credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support the Medium model risk level and Medium decision consequence classification. Model use for regulatory submission accepted.",
